<#import "../macro/global.ftl" as global>
<@global.main pageCss="${css.about_assurance}" pageJavascript="${js.assurance}" activeNav="" activeLeftNav="" title="安全保障">

<div class="risk-flow-container">
    <ul class="quick-top-link page-width">
        <li class="guide"><a href="/about/guide">新手指引</a></li>
        <li class="risk active"><a href="/about/risk-flow">风控流程</a></li>
        <li class="assure "><a href="/about/assurance">安全保障</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="main-banner">
        <div class="page-width">
            <img src="${staticServer}/images/sign/assure/risk-bar.jpg" alt="风控流程">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-examination-box bg-white clearfix">
    <div class="page-width">
        <div class="column-title-ac"><i></i>项目预审<i></i> </div>
        <div class="project-info-list">
        <dl>
            <dt><em>1</em> 接单咨询</dt>
            <dd>客户交房产证或车本、机动车登记证复印件，身份证复印件，业务部电话咨询客户情况</dd>
        </dl>
            <dl>
                <dt><em>2</em> 电话询值</dt>
                <dd>风控部电话咨询评估公司、房产或车辆中介，询问房产或车辆价值，出具电话询值单</dd>
            </dl>
            <dl>
                <dt><em>3</em> 司法核档</dt>
                <dd>客户交房产证或车本、机动车登记证复印件，身份证复印件，业务部电话咨询客户情况</dd>
            </dl>
            <dl>
                <dt><em>6</em> 风控预审</dt>
                <dd>风控部出具预审表给业务部门，确认可以继续跟单</dd>
            </dl>
            <dl>
                <dt><em>5</em> 建委核档</dt>
                <dd>风控部到房屋所在地建委审核房屋档案或机动车辆管理所审核车辆档案，确定抵押物无其他在先他项权利</dd>
            </dl>
            <dl>
                <dt><em>4</em> 转单意见</dt>
                <dd>银行咨询部出具转单意见，确定客户第二还款来源</dd>
            </dl>
        </div>
        <div class="ellipse-shape"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-width margin-top25">
        <div class="column-title-ac">项目二审</div>
        <div class="project-examine-two">
            <div class="square-box-info">
                <i class="triangle"><em></em></i>
                <dl>
                    <dt>1、客户面访</dt>
                    <dd>业务部、风控部约谈客户，根据提供情况：审核银行的批贷流程与期限，填写核行笔录</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>

            <div class="square-box-info">
                <i class="triangle"><em></em></i>
                <dl>
                    <dt>2、材料初审</dt>
                    <dd>风控部给客户下发材料清单，收集客户原件；原件收集后，核原件后做扫描件</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>

            <div class="square-box-info">
                <i class="triangle"><em></em></i>
                <dl>
                    <dt>3、银行核证</dt>
                    <dd>如果是过桥贷或者垫资业务，风控部需要上门审核后手银行的批贷流程与期限，填写核行笔录</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>

            <div class="square-box-info">
                <i class="triangle"><em></em></i>
                <dl>
                    <dt>4、上门家访</dt>
                    <dd>风控部上门家访，拍抵押物照片，填写现场询值单，核实户口，租赁以及居住者情况</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>

            <div class="square-box-info">
                <i class="triangle"><em></em></i>
                <dl>
                    <dt>5、陪打征信</dt>
                    <dd>风控部陪客户去央行征信中心打印征信报告</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="square-box-info">
                <i class="triangle"><em></em></i>
                <dl>
                    <dt>6、风控复审</dt>
                    <dd>风控部出具预审表给业务部门，确认可以继续跟单</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
        <div class="ellipse-shape-center">
            <div class="squareNum">1</div>
            <div class="squareNum">2</div>
            <div class="squareNum">3</div>
            <div class="squareNum">4</div>
            <div class="squareNum">5</div>
            <div class="squareNum">6</div>
            <div class="vertical-line"></div>

        </div>
            <div class="axis-center"></div>
    </div>
</div>

    <div class="bg-white project-examination-box clearfix">
        <div class="page-width">
            <div class="column-title-ac"><i></i>项目终审<i></i> </div>
            <div class="project-examine-last">
                <dl>
                    <dt><em><img src="${staticServer}/images/sign/assure/end01.png" alt="风控流程"></em>材料复核</dt>
                    <dd>总经理助理核实借款材料与风控报告的一致性</dd>
                </dl>
                <dl>
                    <dt><em><img src="${staticServer}/images/sign/assure/end02.png" alt="风控流程"></em>量化评级</dt>
                    <dd>对应拓天速贷系统，量化借款人的安全等级与借款额度</dd>
                </dl>
                <dl>
                    <dt><em><img src="${staticServer}/images/sign/assure/end03.png" alt="风控流程"></em>终审上会</dt>
                    <dd>总经理办公会审核材料，综合评判，确定项目是否通过，一票否决制</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
         </div>

     </div>

    <div class="page-width margin-top25">
    </div>
</@global.main>